-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/tcw-wins-verdict-on-fiduciary-duty-breach-claim-in-trial-against-gundlach.html
Jeffrey Gundlach  was found liable
for breaching his fiduciary duty to TCW Group Inc., the asset-
management firm that fired him in December 2009.  To contact the reporter on this story:
